# Frontend — Portfolio

> Full reference: `TECH_CONVENTIONS.md`

## Layout

```
src/
├── features/
│   ├── alignment/ # mini-game (desktop md+)
│   └── ambient/   # background paw prints
├── components/    # sections + shared/
├── constants/     # shared copy/data
├── contexts/      # providers in App.tsx / index.tsx
├── hooks/         # shared hooks
├── motion/        # shared motion helpers
├── types/         # cross-feature enums/types
├── utils/         # shared utils (cn)
├── App.tsx
└── index.css
```

**Colocate** hooks, utils, constants, types, and contexts with their owner. Promote to top-level folders only when reused across unrelated features, or when a provider mounts in `App.tsx` / `index.tsx`. Cross-cutting app behaviors go under `features/`. Component-specific types stay in that component folder (e.g. `Button.type.ts`).

## Code

- No `any`. Props: `ComponentNameProps`. Fixed-choice inputs → **enum** (not string unions).
- Cross-feature enums/types → `src/types/`. Component enums → co-located `*.type.ts`.
- Props order: required → optional; vars → callbacks; alphabetical within each group (types, destructuring, JSX).
- Imports: external → internal → relative → assets. Named exports; barrel from `components/shared`.
- Copy in `*.const.ts` — not hardcoded in components. Reuse `components/shared/` and `Section`.
- Tailwind + semantic tokens (`ink`, `bg`, `accent`, `line`). Theme via `ThemeProvider` in `src/contexts`.
- `useCallback` / `useMemo` only when justified. No `console.log`.

## New section checklist

- [ ] Data in feature `*.const.ts` or shared `src/constants/`
- [ ] `Section` + unique `id`; navbar link if needed
- [ ] Shared UI reused; light + dark checked
- [ ] `npm run build` passes
